gameMsgFormInfo.text: You can use the LEFT or RIGHT buttons at the bottom right of the screen to move. The A and D keys are alternative methods to move around the room.

arguments.string: label=contentText text="Use the TEXT BOX to type the phrase 'put the patient on the monitors' and select the task from the list that appears."

gameMsgFormInfo.text: The procedure resident is trained to perform any item in the secondary survey.

gameMsgFormInfo.text: Say the phrase 'Order one unit of saline' or type the keywords 'one liter normal saline'.
gameMsgFormInfo.title: Ordering Fluids

arguments.string: label=contentText text="Say the phrase 'Order one unit of saline' or type the keywords 'one liter normal saline'."

gameMsgFormInfo.text: On the right side of the screen, click the 'Recent Orders' tab or say the phrase 'What are you doing?' Click the tab again to close.
gameMsgFormInfo.title: Recent Orders

arguments.string: label=contentText text="On the right side of the screen, click the 'Recent Orders' tab or say the phrase 'What are you doing?' Click the tab again to close."

gameMsgFormInfo.text: If you lose track of what your team is doing, or you need them to refocus on a new task you can stop all pending orders. Try that now by saying or typing the phrase 'Stop Everything'.

arguments.string: label=titleBarText text="How To Cancel Pending Orders"

gameMsgFormInfo.text: Try to avoid institutional slang for your orders. If a command is not recognized, try phrasing it another way.
gameMsgFormInfo.title: General Orders

arguments.string: label=contentText text="Try to avoid institutional slang for your orders. If a command is not recognized, try phrasing it another way."

gameMsgFormInfo.text: The 'W' and 'S' keys will move you closer and further away from the patient. Alternatively, the 'Bedside / Team View' button found at the bottom right will toggle your distance from the bedside.
gameMsgFormInfo.title: Bedside / Team View

arguments.string: label=contentText text="The 'W' and 'S' keys will move you closer and further away from the patient. Alternatively, the 'Bedside / Team View' button found at the bottom right will toggle your distance from the bedside."

gameMsgFormInfo.text: When speaking to the patient, you can phrase your questions directly. For example, type or say the phrase 'Can you tell me your name?'.

arguments.string: label=contentText text="When speaking to the patient, you can phrase your questions directly. For example, type or say the phrase 'Can you tell me your name?'."

gameMsgFormInfo.text: The procedure resident can examine a variety of the patient's body regions. Say or type 'palpate the trachea' to examine Henry's trachea.

gameMsgFormInfo.text: If you have a microphone connected, press and hold the SPACEBAR and say the phrase 'Call for an Xray'. If not, you can type the keywords 'call for an xray' in the text box.

arguments.string: label=contentText text="If you have a microphone connected, press and hold the SPACEBAR and say the phrase 'Call for an Xray'. If not, you can type the keywords 'call for an xray' in the text box."
